title: League of Legends World Championship Brings in Nearly a Million Concurrent Viewers
text:
League of Legends World Championship Brings in Nearly a Million Concurrent Viewers 
Published By: Gamespot.com - Today 
The League of Legends World Championships kicked off earlier this week in Paris, raking in nearly one million concurrent viewers on Twitch. ...
